# Purpose:
# - Exclude unnecessary local files from the backend Docker build context.
#
# Should exclude:
# - Virtual environments
# - Cache directories
# - Test artifacts
# - Local environment files and secrets
#
# Notes:
# - Smaller build contexts improve build speed and reduce accidental leakage.

__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.venv/
.git
.gitignore
.idea/